descriptionHTML:
Stylish analog Watch Face for Android Wear devices.
All settings are changeable through the wearables configuration options.


★Tap on Watch Face to cycle through themes
★Temperature information based on current location
★Use the wearable configuration app to choose a theme
★Use the wearable configuration app to choose between C or F temperature units
★Choose between Light Blue, Red, Lime Green, White and Monochrome White themes
★Works on both round and square devices
★Supports ambient mode
